) accounts and the study of voucher material listed in 
<tableCitation id="3F19B8E83902FF88610061EFF7C4FB64" box="[378,471,1164,1190]" captionStart="TABLE 1" captionStartId="5.[264,352,365,389]" captionText="TABLE 1. Pinnotherid material examined." pageId="4" pageNumber="37">
Table 
